                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - F
                   ====================================

                            Fernandez Must Die
                            ==================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x Pl. 1" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(47301,255)"}         47301,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Lives = x Pl. 2" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(47290,255)"}         47290,x (x= 1-255)

                         Another one I cracked back in my youth :)

                         Rastan.
@endnode
